@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fwdcsa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.24) / (tmp + 0.57 - v1 + 0.86)) / ((v1 + 0.83 - tmp + 0.29) + (v0 + 0.53 + tmp + 0.67)))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v0 + 0.23) + (v2 + 0.10 * tmp + 0.67)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.89)) + (wp.sin(v0 + 0.05) / wp.exp(tmp + 0.66)))
    v2 = (v2 - v2)
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.23 / v2 + 0.31)) * wp.abs(v2))
    v0 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.63 + v0 + 0.59) * wp.cos(v2 + 0.93)))
    data[tid] = v0
